Package: PostcodesioR
Type: Package
Title: API Wrapper Around Postcodes.io (Free UK Postcode Lookup and Geocoder)
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: c(person("Eryk", "Walczak", 
                  email = "eryk.j.walczak@gmail.com", 
